/td><td><p>20</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Intelligence Corps</p></td><td><p>21</p></td><td><p>24</p></td><td><p>24</p></td><td><p>24</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Total</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>557</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>579</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>590</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>578</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><br /><p>Requirements for professionally qualified officer intake into the regular trained strength</p><br /><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Cap badge</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2015-16 Requirement</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2016-17 Requirement</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2017-18 Requirement</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2018-19 Requirement</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Royal Army Chaplains Department</p></td><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>10</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Royal Army Medical Corps Professionally Qualified Officer</p></td><td><p>43</p></td><td><p>38</p></td><td><p>38</p></td><td><p>38</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Adjutant General’s Corps(Army Legal Services)</p></td><td><p>7</p></td><td><p>7</p></td><td><p>7</p></td><td><p>7</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Royal Army Dental Corps</p></td><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>6</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Royal Army Veterinary Corps</p></td><td><p>4</p></td><td><p>4</p></td><td><p>4</p></td><td><p>5</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Queen Alexandra’s Royal Army Nursing Corps</p></td><td><p>22</p></td><td><p>22</p></td><td><p>22</p></td><td><p>22</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Total</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>92</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>87</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>87</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>88</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><br /><br /><p>In addition intake requirements for Regular to Regular Re-joiners are:</p><br /><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Financial Year</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2015-16 Requirement</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2016-17 Requirement</strong></p></td><td><p>